org.apache.jena.sparql.function.js

Class NV

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jena.sparql.function.js.NV
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RDFJS

    public class NV
extends Object
implements RDFJS
    General representation of an NodeValue for JavaScript. Conversion is to native types where possible, otherwise NV. NV.toString of a URI returns the uri as a string so NV works naturally in Java/JavaScript.
    See Also:
    fromNodeValue(org.apache.jena.sparql.expr.NodeValue), toNodeValue(java.lang.Object), RDFTerm2Json, for one way conversion JSON.

    • Method Detail

      • fromNodeValue

        public static Object fromNodeValue(NodeValue nv)
        Map an ARQ NodeValue to java/Nashorn/GraalVM representation of a JavaScript object. Native JavaScript types supported are null, string, number and boolean. Otherwise a NV is returned.

      • toNodeValue

        public static NodeValue toNodeValue(Object r)
        Map a java/Nashorn/GraalVM representation of a JavaScript object to an ARQ NodeValue. Identified types are null, string, number and boolean and also NV returned by the JavaScript code.
